<cell id="cell-0"><cell_type>markdown</cell_type># Stage 1 Training — Cross-Embodiment Shared Latent Space (Multi-Robot)

Yan et al. (2026) — shared E_h / E_X / D_X + per-robot E_r / D_r.

**Drive files needed (`MyDrive/AIST-hand/`):**
| File | Description |
|------|-------------|
| `hograspnet_abl14_r6.csv` | Human poses, 6D repr |
| `data/processed/hagrid_dong_r6.csv` | HaGRID extra human anchors (open/fist) |
| `dex-urdf/` | Shadow URDF + kinematics |
| `valid_robot_poses_eigengrasp_dong_r6.npz` | Shadow DONG cache (10M poses, ~6 GB) |
| `valid_robot_poses_allegro_dong.npz` | Allegro DONG cache (10M poses, ~7.4 GB) |

> Both DONG caches are pinned to CPU RAM (not VRAM). Shadow+Allegro together = ~13 GB RAM.
> Colab Pro/Pro+ (25 GB RAM) required for multi-robot. For single-robot use the `ROBOTS` dict below.

**Runtime:** GPU — `Runtime > Change runtime type > T4 GPU`</cell id="cell-0">
